  "What is 'hydrostatic pressure'?": "",
  "The pressure inside a hydraulic cylinder": "",
  "Pressure due to flowing water": "",
  "The pressure exerted by a fluid at rest due to the weight of the fluid above, given by P = rho*g*h": "",
  "The atmospheric pressure at sea level": "",
  "Hydrostatic pressure is the pressure in a fluid at rest due to gravity. It increases linearly with depth: P = rho*g*h.": "",
  "What is 'density'?": "",
  "The weight of an object": "",
  "The volume per unit mass": "",
  "The hardness of a material": "",
  "The mass per unit volume of a substance, rho = m/V, measured in kg/m^3": "",
